# Runtime data + local artifacts (not source).
# NOTE: .gitignore does NOT support inline (trailing) comments — a comment
# after a pattern on the same line makes the whole line a literal path and the
# pattern silently stops matching. Keep comments on their own lines.
# uploaded PDFs + generated screenshots
var/
# uvicorn / retry logs
*.log
